{"type":"message","id":"1f29ece4","parentId":"2b408005","timestamp":"2026-05-26T07:31:36.954Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me verify the changes look correct.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的主人，已经改好了！我来总结一下改了什么：\n\n**根本原因：** Unity batchmode 即使流水线内部步骤失败（比如 git pull 失败了），退出码依然是 0，所以之前认为「退出码 0 = 成功」漏掉了错误。\n\n**改进：** 在热更流水线执行完成后，不再只看 Unity 退出码，还会额外扫描日志文件，检测以下关键字：\n- `error CS\\d+:` — C# 编译报错\n- `git更新失败` — 流水线内的 git pull 失败\n- `Build completed with` — 构建报告有 errors\n\n匹配到任何一个 → 视为失败，发 `hotupdate-fail` 通知（开发群 @兵王）\n无匹配 + 退出码 0 → 视为成功，发 `hotupdate-ok` 通知\n\n逻辑已经更新到 TOOLS.md 和 MEMORY.md 了，下次跑热更就会自动带上错误检测🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":144,"output":214,"cacheRead":33280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33638,"cost":{"input":0.00002016,"output":0.00005992,"cacheRead":0.00093184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00101192}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779780693221,"responseId":"b189f4c3-a9fc-4e68-8062-fd99b8f6b83a"}}
