\n,TriggerParams,,,,,,,,type,\"(list#sep=,),int\",,类型,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,props,\"(list#sep=|),string\",,参数,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,target,\"(list#sep=,),int\",,目标,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,targetProps,\"(list#sep=|),string\",,目标参数,\r\r\n,slotOne,,,,,,,,id,int,,道具id,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,count,int,,数量,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,weight,int,,权重,\r\r\n,ConditionParams,,,,,,,,type,\"(list#sep=,),int\",,类型,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,props,\"(list#sep=|),string\",,参数,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,target,\"(list#sep=,),int\",,目标,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,targetProps,\"(list#sep=|),string\",,目标参数,\r\r\n,RewardData,,,,,,,,id,int,,道具id,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,count,int,,数量,\r\r\n,TargetParams,,,,,,,,target,int,,目标计数,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,type1,int,,目标类型1,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,type2,int,,目标类型2,\r\r\n,EventbonusData,,,,,,,,target,int,,阶段,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,itemId,int,,奖励id,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,count,int,,道具数量,\r\r\n,slotMore,,,,,,,,id,int,,道具id,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,count,int,,数量,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,probability,int,,概率,\r\r\n,RechargeRebateData,,,,,,,,mailId,int,,邮件id,\r\r\n,,,,,,,,,rewards,\"(list#sep=|),(RewardData#sep=,)\",,奖品道具列表,","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779780933765}}
{"type":"message","id":"bfb73ecd","parentId":"19129527","timestamp":"2026-05-26T07:35:42.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete understanding of the Luban config system. Let me now create the skill.\n\n**Summary of the Luban system in the SoloConfig submodule:**\n\n1. **Schema definition files:**\n   - `Datas/__tables__.xlsx` - Table definitions (name, full_name, input file, mode, group, etc.)\n   - `Datas/__beans__.xlsx` - Complex type/struct definitions\n   - `Datas/__enums__.xlsx` - Enum type definitions\n   - `Defines/builtin.xml` - Built-in types (vector2, vector3, vector4)\n\n2. **Data files:**\n   - Each xlsx in `Datas/` contains table data with schema read from header rows\n   - Two formats:\n     - **List format** (like Card.xlsx): Row 1 = `##var`, `##type`, `##group`, Row 2 = comment, Row3+ = data\n     - **Key-value format** (like Common.xlsx): Row 1 = `##column#var`, `##type`, `##group`, Row 2 = comments, Row3+ = key-value pairs\n\n3. **Tools:**\n   - `xlsx2csv/xlsx2csv.exe` - Convert xlsx to CSV\n   - `Luban` - Excel data processing tool (most likely regenerated by the main project's build pipeline)\n\nNow, the skill needs to handle \"给表格添加字段\" which means adding a new field/column to an existing config table.\n\n**The practical workflow:**\n\n1. User says \"给Card表加一个abc字段, 类型是int\"\n2. Determine which xlsx file corresponds to the table (from `__tables__.xlsx`)\n3. Read the xlsx header to understand existing columns\n4. Add new column to the xlsx file (using a script)\n5. Fill in default values for existing rows\n6. The main project's Unity build pipeline will regenerate the C#/Go code\n\nFor xlsx manipulation, I should create a script since manually handling xlsx from the assistant isn't practical. Let me write a Node.js script using the `xlsx` npm package.\n\nActually, wait. Let me check if `xlsx` is available.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_iyaMw1