{"type":"message","id":"141dfded","parentId":"71f6bc65","timestamp":"2026-05-26T07:35:50.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No xlsx package. I'll install it. Let me now create the skill.\n\nLet me plan the skill structure:\n\n1. **Skill name:** `solo-config-field`\n2. **Skill directory:** Under OpenClaw plugin-skills: `~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/solo-config-field/`\n3. **Resources:**\n   - `SKILL.md` - The skill instructions\n   - `scripts/add_field.mjs` - Node.js script to add a field to an xlsx table\n   - `references/luban-format.md` - Reference for Luban Excel format\n\nLet me write the script and SKILL.md.\n\nActually, given the complexity of xlsx manipulation, I should install the `xlsx` npm package first and write a comprehensive script. Let me also note that the skill directory should be created under `~/.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\solo-config-field\\`.\n\nLet me first install xlsx, then create the script and SKILL.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我安装 xlsx 库，然后创建技能目录和脚本。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9vr57Ih5zPaTcmtpBKrT8132","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cmd /c \"cd /d C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace && npm install xlsx\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":93,"output":308,"cacheRead":111616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112017,"cost":{"input":0.00001302,"output":0.00008624,"cacheRead":0.0031252479999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032245079999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779780945925,"responseId":"c5e87ef7-7cbd-4bd6-951d-62fad40837fd"}}
