{"type":"message","id":"8112afb2","parentId":"84a3dc3b","timestamp":"2026-05-26T07:38:43.641Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, everything is in place. Let me also verify the SKILL.md content and the skills-manifest.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好了，技能已经创建完成！来总结一下：\n\n## 新增技能：`solo-config-field`\n\n**位置：** `~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/solo-config-field/`\n\n### 技能文件\n- **SKILL.md** — 技能说明，含表格格式定义、字段类型参考、操作流程\n- **scripts/add_field.mjs** — 核心脚本，用 Node.js 给 xlsx 表加字段\n\n### 支持两种表格格式\n| 格式 | 特征 | 示例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **KV 格式** | `##column#var` 开头，每行一个配置项 | Common.xlsx |\n| **列表格式** | `##var` 开头，每行一条记录 | Card.xlsx, Buff.xlsx |\n\n### 使用方式\n```bash\nnode <技能目录>/scripts/add_field.mjs <表名> <字段名> <类型> [--group c|s|e] [--desc \"注释\"] [--default \"值\"] [--after 前字段]\n```\n\n### 示例\n```bash\n# 给 Card 表追加 int 字段\nnode add_field.mjs Card testField int --group c,s\n\n# 给 Common 表加 float 字段\nnode add_field.mjs Common testField float --group c --default 0\n\n# 给 Buff 表插入列表字段（在 type 列后面）\nnode add_field.mjs Buff newField \"(list#sep=,),int\" --after type\n```\n\n添加完字段后需要手动跑 Unity BuildPipeline 生成代码，以及更新客户端/服务端逻辑。\n\n主人试试看？直接说「给X表加个y字段」我就能调脚本处理🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":150,"output":393,"cacheRead":127872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128415,"cost":{"input":0.000021000000000000002,"output":0.00011004000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003580416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003711456}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779781117831,"responseId":"40e4485a-c487-45e6-9dfd-bf6937213738"}}
