{"type":"message","id":"4ccf3a70","parentId":"c76ca8c1","timestamp":"2026-05-26T07:48:50.398Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the HeroSkin.xlsx structure clearly. Let me analyze:\n\n**Fields (##var row):**\n1. `id` - int\n2. `HeroId` - \"(list#sep=,),int\" (数组)\n3. `name` - string\n4. `down_desc` - string\n5. `SkinIcon` - \"(list#sep=|),(list#sep=,),string\" (嵌套数组)\n6. `Skin_FX` - \"(list#sep=|),(list#sep=,),string\"\n7. `twoPlayerIcon` - string\n8. `SkinSpineAni` - \"(list#sep=,),string\" (数组，逗号分隔)\n9. `inTimeline` - string\n10. `changeTimeline` - string\n11. `heroBorderFX` - string\n12. `cardFX` - string\n13. `head_icon` - string\n14. `deck_icon` - string\n15. `replace_eft_change` - string\n16. `replace_eft_death` - string\n17. `replace_voice_begin` - \"int?#(ref=TbVoice)\" (可选int，引用TbVoice表)\n18. `replace_voice_in` - \"(list#sep=,),int#(ref=TbVoice)\" (int数组，引用TbVoice)\n19. `replace_voice_change` - \"(list#sep=,),int#(ref=TbVoice)\"\n20. `replace_voice_death` - \"(list#sep=,),int#(ref=TbVoice)\"\n21. `replace_voice_win` - \"(list#sep=,),int#(ref=TbVoice)\"\n22. `replace_voice_game` - \"(list#sep=,),int#(ref=TbVoice)\"\n\nOK, so the Luban type system in this project is quite rich. Let me summarize all the type patterns I've seen:\n\n**Basic Types:**\n- `int` - 整数\n- `float` - 浮点数\n- `long` - 长整数\n- `string` - 字符串\n- `bool` - 布尔值\n\n**Array Types (Luban uses \"(container#option1=val1,option2=val2),elementType\"):**\n- `(list#sep=,),int` — 逗号分隔的整数列表\n- `(list#sep=,),float` — 逗号分隔的浮点数列表\n- `(list#sep=|),string` — 竖线分隔的字符串列表\n- `(set#sep=,),int` — 逗号分隔的整数集合（元素唯一）\n- `(list#sep=,),string` — 逗号分隔的字符串列表\n- `(list#sep=|),(list#sep=,),string` — 嵌套数组：竖线分隔，每个元素是逗号分隔的字符串列表\n\n**Modifiers:**\n- `?#` — 可选字段（nullable），如 `int?#(ref=TbVoice)`\n- `#(ref=TableName)` — 引用其他表的 ID\n\n**复合类型:**\n- 枚举名（如 `HapticType`，定义在 `__enums__.xlsx`）\n- Bean名（如 `BuffParams`，定义在 `__beans__.xlsx`）\n\n对于主人说的「Offset 表示动画偏移量，数组类型」，通常有两种可能的含义：\n1. 一个简单的 float 列表，如 `(list#sep=,),float`\n2. 或者一个 vector3（如果偏移量是三维坐标），但 vector3 是内置的 bean 类型，在 builtin.xml 中定义为 `float x, float y, float z`\n\n不过从主人说的\"数组类型\"来看，更可能是简单的一维 float 数组。如果是在 Spine 动画中的偏移量，可能是 x 偏移和 y 偏移值，也就是 `(list#sep=,),float`。\n\n让我更新 SKILL.md，补充更详细的数据类型参考。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了！HeroSkin 表的数据类型挺丰富的。让我全面分析一下 Luban 的类型系统。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_rQAMsXr5NbObmcIjb24V0458","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cmd /c \"cd /d E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\config\\SoloConfig && xlsx2csv\\xlsx2csv.exe Datas\\Buff.xlsx 2>nul | head -10\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1222,"output":999,"cacheRead":86272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88493,"cost":{"input":0.00017108000000000002,"output":0.00027972,"cacheRead":0.0024156159999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0028664159999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779781719640,"responseId":"a2d5cf70-32f1-4a87-b40a-d519c3d9dfbc"}}
