{"type":"message","id":"79121aae","parentId":"0a9ee32b","timestamp":"2026-05-26T07:49:27.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me verify the SKILL.md is complete and looks good. Let me also clean up the Buff.xlsx data as it was very large and might have been printed to the conversation. Let me update the skills-manifest version since this skill was just updated with new type reference content.\n\nActually the skills-manifest already has the version at 1. The skill was just created so that's fine.\n\nLet me now verify the file and then inform the user about the answer to their specific question about Offset and array types.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好了，我完整学习了 Luban 类型系统，已经更新到 SKILL.md 里了。\n\n关于你说的 **HeroSkin 表加 Offset 字段，数组类型**：\n\n根据 HeroSkin 的现有字段类型来看，**动画偏移量**最合适的写法是：\n\n```\n(列表类型#分隔符=逗号),float类型\n```\n\n即：\n\n```bash\nnode add_field.mjs HeroSkin Offset \"(list#sep=,),float\" --group c,s --desc \"动画偏移量\"\n```\n\n在单元格里填例如 `0.5,1.2`（x偏移,y偏移）或 `0.5,1.2,0.0`（x,y,z）。\n\n**完整类型速查：**\n\n| 你想要 | 写法 |\n|--------|------|\n| 整数数组 | `(list#sep=,),int` |\n| 📌 **浮点数数组** | `**(list#sep=,),float**` |\n| 字符串数组 | `(list#sep=,),string` |\n| 逗号分隔 | `#sep=,` |\n| 竖线分隔 | `#sep=|` |\n| 数组 + 引用 | `(list#sep=,),int#(ref=TbVoice)` |\n\n要不要我现在就帮你把 `Offset` 字段加上？🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":165,"output":387,"cacheRead":151168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151720,"cost":{"input":0.000023100000000000002,"output":0.00010836000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0042327039999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004364163999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779781760321,"responseId":"08ddd135-5061-4eff-8411-ee743cfe3413"}}
