{"type":"message","id":"397b366e","parentId":"860c2917","timestamp":"2026-05-26T07:54:30.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"✅ 字段添加成功了！\n\n现在有 24 列，最后一列是 Offset，类型是 `(list#sep=,),int`。\n\n主人，已搞定 ✅ **HeroSkin.xlsx** 已添加 `Offset` 字段：\n\n```\n类型：(list#sep=,),int   (整数数组，逗号分隔)\n分组：c,s\n注释：动画偏移量\n```\n\n需要填数据的话，在单元格里写例如 `100,200`（x偏移,y偏移），或者 `100,200,50`（x,y,z）就行。\n\n后续还需要的步骤（你手动搞定）：\n1. 🏗️ 跑 Unity BuildPipeline 的 Luban 代码生成\n2. 💻 更新客户端/服务端代码引用新字段\n3. 📦 提交 SoloConfig 子模块变更","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":120,"output":174,"cacheRead":111104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111398,"cost":{"input":0.000016800000000000002,"output":0.00004872,"cacheRead":0.003110912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003176432}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779782066599,"responseId":"44bc4a82-15bd-4012-9658-ae24c2f51ac5"}}
