{"type":"message","id":"136360d2","parentId":"7d89c9aa","timestamp":"2026-05-26T08:01:25.609Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说：每次修改前，先更新表格（git pull），如果本地打开着表格就关闭。\n\n这是指在 SoloConfig 子模块里修改 xlsx 文件前，需要：\n1. 先 `git pull` 更新 SoloConfig 子模块\n2. 检查是否有进程打开了 xlsx 文件（如 Excel.exe），如果有则关闭\n\n我应该把这个步骤加到 SKILL.md 和 add_field.mjs 脚本中，作为前置步骤。最合理的方式是：\n\n1. 在 add_field.mjs 脚本中添加初始化步骤：\n   - `git -C SoloConfig pull` 更新子模块\n   - 检查是否有 Excel.exe 进程打开了相关文件，如果有则 kill\n\n2. 更新 SKILL.md 文档\n\n让我来实现这个逻辑。\n\n实际上，对于 git pull，SoloConfig 是子模块，需要在子模块目录内执行 `git pull`。而且主人是在 `nightoffullmoon` 主仓库里，子模块的路径是 `client/config/SoloConfig`。\n\n对于关闭 Excel，可以用 `Get-Process excel` 然后检查是否打开了特定文件，或者直接 `Stop-Process -Name excel` 关掉所有 Excel 进程。但更安全的是只关掉打开了目标文件的 Excel 进程。\n\n实际上，检查具体哪个进程打开了哪个文件比较复杂。简单的做法是关掉所有 Excel.exe 进程，因为如果有人在编辑表格，就应该保存关闭后再让脚本修改。\n\n让我更新脚本和 SKILL.md。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，加在脚本里作为自动前置步骤最靠谱。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ER45Vm9cacFqCGlh9O8N3570","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\solo-config-field\\scripts\\add_field.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"import { readFileSync, writeFileSync, existsSync } from 'fs';","newText":"import { readFileSync, writeFileSync, existsSync, execSync } from 'child_process';"},{"oldText":"import { readFileSync, writeFileSync, existsSync } from 'fs';","newText":"import { readFileSync, writeFileSync, existsSync } from 'fs';"},{"oldText":"import { readFileSync, writeFileSync, existsSync } from 'fs';","newText":"import { readFileSync, writeFileSync, existsSync } from 'fs';"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":12975,"output":544,"cacheRead":98304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111823,"cost":{"input":0.0018165000000000002,"output":0.00015232,"cacheRead":0.002752512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004721332}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779782475895,"responseId":"a1647d2c-5a3