{"type":"message","id":"10fd587a","parentId":"ce2dfe88","timestamp":"2026-05-26T08:44:03.541Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The hot update failed due to git pull failure in a submodule within the pipeline. The child session already sent the failure notification to the group chat and detected the error using our new log scanning. Let me now inform the owner about the result.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"❌ **测试包热更失败**\n\n这次编译失败检测立功了！Unity 退出码是 0 但流水线内子仓库 `git pull` 失败，被日志扫描抓住了。\n\n**错误原因：** 流水线内部拉取战斗模块子仓库时失败（`git更新失败`，位置在 `PullBattleModuleForce`），主仓库虽然 pull 了 47 个文件更新，但子模块没同步上。\n\n**已经做了：**\n- ✅ 群通知已发 @兵王\n- ❌ 失败通知已发出\n\n**建议手动修复后重试：**\n\n```bash\ncd E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\ngit submodule update --init --recursive\n```\n\n或者手动进子仓库目录拉一下，然后再跑一次「更新测试服」🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":115273,"output":223,"cacheRead":1920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117416,"cost":{"input":0.01613822,"output":0.00006244,"cacheRead":0.00005376,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016254420000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779785033731,"responseId":"5f6862a6-c11a-46b3-a214-3a962c1ad900"}}
