{"type":"message","id":"f5583ecc","parentId":"746fccee","timestamp":"2026-05-26T08:44:20.779Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说以后热更失败的时候只私聊他通知，不用在群里发失败消息。\n\n我需要更新热更流程，让失败时只通知主人（群通知模板 `hotupdate-fail` → 改成私聊通知）。成功时仍然在群里 @兵王。\n\n让我更新 TOOLS.md 和 MEMORY.md 中的热更流程说明。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，改一下规则——失败私聊，成功群通知。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_A9qVhQwp2rHGocLOoTqp6131","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"**反馈要求:** 每个步骤执行中状态变化都要通过飞书消息及时反馈，包括：开始执行、执行中（等待）、执行完成/失败。不要让主人干等。\n\n**更新完成后:** 用 `node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs` 发群消息通知（不要用 sessions_send，那只能发私聊）。\n成功命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok`\n失败命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-fail`\n⚠️ 不要在命令行里拼含引号的 @ 文本，改用模板名（hotupdate-ok / hotupdate-fail）避免转义问题","newText":"**反馈要求:** 每个步骤执行中状态变化都要通过飞书消息及时反馈，包括：开始执行、执行中（等待）、执行完成/失败。不要让主人干等。\n\n**更新完成后:**\n- ✅ **成功** → 用 `node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs` 发群消息通知（@兵王）\n  命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok`\n- ❌ **失败** → 只私聊通知主人，**不在群里发失败消息**\n  使用 sessions_send 私聊通知主人结果\n⚠️ 不要在命令行里拼含引号的 @ 文本，改用模板名（hotupdate-ok）避免转义问题"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6948,"output":564,"cacheRead":110976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118488,"cost":{"input":0.00097272,"output":0.00015792,"cacheRead":0.003107328,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004237968}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779785054293,"responseId":"981b843d-1aba-47ba-900a-0fdeafcb1f79"}}
