{"type":"message","id":"a6443edf","parentId":"1d9c36b1","timestamp":"2026-05-26T08:44:27.780Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"以后失败的时候单独私聊我就行\" - meaning I should private message the owner (主人) when it fails. Since we're in a direct chat with the owner (this IS the owner, Yousan/叶枝君), I should just use sessions_send to notify the owner when the sub-agent reports failure.\n\nActually, looking at the current setup, the sub-agent already notifies the owner via sessions_send. The issue was that it ALSO sent a group failure notification. Now I've updated the instructions to only send group messages on success and only private message the owner on failure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"改好了！以后更新测试服的规则：\n\n| 结果 | 通知方式 |\n|------|---------|\n| ✅ 成功 | 发开发群 @兵王 |\n| ❌ 失败 | **只私聊你**，不在群里发 |\n\n下次跑热更就会按新规则来了🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":46,"output":188,"cacheRead":118784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119018,"cost":{"input":0.00000644,"output":0.000052640000000000004,"cacheRead":0.003325952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003385032}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779785063829,"responseId":"a88438e7-1a4a-4b1c-b55a-b95e6fe36d0b"}}
