{"type":"message","id":"2c987928","parentId":"4be75206","timestamp":"2026-05-26T09:31:40.954Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_J8HX7i8TctKb1kJY87lH7095","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"unity-mcp\nModel Context Protocol server for Unity.\nVersion 1.1.0 published 2025-03-14 by artmann\nMaintainers: artmann\nKeywords: typescript mcp unity blazing-fast claude\nhttps://npm.im/unity-mcp\n\nanklebreaker-unity-mcp\nUnity MCP Server — Multi-agent MCP server for Unity Editor, designed for Claude Cowork. By AnkleBreaker Studio.\nVersion 2.29.0 published 2026-05-21 by anklebreaker-studio\nMaintainers: anklebreaker-studio\nhttps://npm.im/anklebreaker-unity-mcp\n\nunity-mcp-cli\nCross-platform CLI tool for AI Game Developer (Skills & MCP). Full AI develop and test loop. Efficient token usage, advanced tools. Creates Unity project, installs plugins, configures tools, and manages HTTP connection with Unity Editor and a game made wi\nVersion 0.75.3 published 2026-05-24 by GitHub Actions\nMaintainers: baizor\nKeywords: cli unity unity ai unity skills unity mcp ai skills ai mcp ai mcp model-context-protocol gamedev game-dev\nhttps://npm.im/unity-mcp-cli\n\n@iflow-mcp/unity-mcp-server\nUnity MCP Server - Simple HTTP-based Unity Editor integration for AI assistants\nVersion 3.1.1 published 2025-12-09 by chatflowdev\nMaintainers: chatflowdev qystart\nKeywords: mcp mcp-server model-context-protocol unity unity3d unity-editor gamedev game-development claude ai ai-tools\nhttps://npm.im/@iflow-mcp/unity-mcp-server\n\nthe-unity-architect\nAn expert Unity AI agent framework: skills, best practices, and utility scripts for AI-assisted Unity development with tools like Antigravity, Cursor, and Unity MCP.\nVersion 1.3.5 published 2026-05-21 by unlince\nMaintainers: unlince\nKeywords: unity unity3d ai-agent cursor antigravity mcp game-development skills best-practices debugging\nhttps://npm.im/the-unity-architect\n\n@akiojin/unity-mcp-server\nMCP server and