{"type":"message","id":"df6d6ebd","parentId":"d49fc34b","timestamp":"2026-05-26T09:37:40.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Unity Editor 已经打开了，项目是 cardv。但 MCP 还没配好。\n\n让我想想其他方式来控制 Unity Play Mode。有两种可能的方案：\n\n1. **通过 Unity Editor 的 C# 脚本执行** — 可以用 Unity 的命令行 `-executeMethod`，但这需要重启 Unity 或者在 batchmode 下运行，不适用。\n\n2. **通过模拟键盘快捷键** — Unity Play Mode 的默认快捷键是 `Ctrl+P` 或直接点击播放按钮。我可以通过 Windows API 给 Unity 窗口发送按键消息。\n\n3. **通过 Unity Editor 的 IPC/管道** — 有些工具比如 Unity Editor 的 EditorApplication API 可以通过进程间通信调用。\n\n我觉得最实际的方式是方法2：找到 Unity 窗口，然后模拟按键或鼠标点击。\n\n或者另一种方式：通过 Unity 的 `-saveProject` 加上执行脚本的方法，但这也需要重启。\n\n让我用 `SendKeys` 或 Windows API 的方法，给 Unity 窗口发送 Ctrl+P（播放快捷键）。\n\n或者，我可以用 `[System.Windows.Forms.SendKeys]` 在 PowerShell 中实现。\n\n但还有一个更简单的方法——可以用 `AutoIt` 或 PowerShell 的 `Add-Type` 来调用 user32.dll 的 `SendMessage` 发送快捷键。\n\n让我试试 PowerShell 的 SendKeys 方法。\n\n实际上，Unity 播放按钮的快捷键是 Ctrl+P（在 Windows 上默认）。\n\n让我通过 PowerShell 的 SendKeys 来模拟。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Unity 已经打开了！让我用快捷键模拟点击播放按钮（Ctrl+P）。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2uEsQTdv0CGpajjR92hY6575","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\_play_unity.ps1","content":"Add-Type -AssemblyName System.Windows.Forms\nAdd-Type -AssemblyName Microsoft.VisualBasic\n\n# Find Unity Editor window and activate it\n$unity = Get-Process unity -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object -First 1\nif ($unity) {\n    Write-Host \"Found Unity Editor (PID: $($unity.Id))\"\n    \n    # Bring Unity window to foreground\n    $sig = '[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern bool SetForegroundWindow(IntPtr hWnd);'\n    $type = Add-Type -MemberDefinition $sig -Name \"Win32SetForeground\" -Namespace Win32Functions -PassThru\n    $type::SetForegroundWindow($unity.MainWindowHandle)\n    \n    Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 500\n    \n    # Send Ctrl+P to play\n    [System.Windows.Forms.SendKeys]::SendWait(\"^(p)\")\n    \n    Write-Host \"Sent Ctrl+P (Play) to Unity Editor\"\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"Unity Editor not running\"\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":65,"output":623,"cacheRead":147200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147888,"cost":{"input":0.000009100000000000001,"output":0.00017444000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0041216,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00430514}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779788250534,"responseId":"4f611bf6-36ba-486a-8ef8-bd4927e35f2d"}}
