{"type":"message","id":"0cf6214a","parentId":"3bac17f9","timestamp":"2026-05-26T11:51:33.618Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说「更新测试服」，客户端热更流水线。重启后第一次跑，需要注意之前的流程更新：\n\n1. 先关 Unity Editor（可能重启后没开）\n2. git pull\n3. git submodule update --init --recursive\n4. 运行热更流水线\n5. 检查编译结果（扫日志关键字）\n6. 成功→群通知 @兵王，失败→私聊通知主人\n\n这是耗时任务，开子 session 处理。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，开始更新测试包🌸"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_i4Ncm3k1vfk5lW5wYyNJ2519","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"更新测试服（客户端热更）\n\n流程：\n1. 检查是否有 Unity 进程在执行 `RunHotUpdatePipeline`（通过进程命令行参数判断），如果有则提示已有流水线在执行，退出任务\n2. 关掉所有已打开的 Unity Editor 进程（kill Unity.exe 进程）\n3. cd E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon 然后 git pull 更新当前分支\n4. git submodule update --init --recursive 更新所有子模块\n5. 运行 E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n6. 等待流水线完成，检查编译结果：\n   - 扫描日志文件 `E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log`\n   - 命令：`powershell -Command \"Select-String -Path 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log' -Pattern 'error CS\\d+:|git更新失败|Build completed with'\"`\n   - 匹配到关键字 → 视为失败\n   - 无匹配 + Unity 退出码 0 → 视为成功\n7. 完成后通知：\n   - ✅ **成功** → 用 node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs 发群消息通知（@兵王）\n     node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok\n   - ❌ **失败** → 只私聊通知主人，**不在群里发**\n8. 用 sessions_send 通知主人结果\n\n⚠️ 注意：\n- 运行 bat 文件直接用 exec 工具执行路径，不要用 cmd /c 或 powershell -Command 包裹\n- 运行 bat 时需要管理员权限（Unity 许可证校验）\n- 默认增量构建模式（不清 Bundles 缓存）\n- 日志文件路径：E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log","label":"hotupdate-client","mode":"run","cleanup":"keep"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2054,"output":658,"cacheRead":148480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151192,"cost":{"input":0.00028756,"output":0.00018424,"cacheRead":0.00415744,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.